data.description: One of a Kind with 270-Degree Water Views! Step into this nearly new 2022 end unit townhouse in the sought-after Woodleaf Hammock community in Lakewood Ranch. Boasting nearly 270 degrees of mesmerizing water views, this home offers a serene retreat.    Inside, you'll find a spacious 3-bedroom layout with a spacious loft and a convenient 2 cars garage. The kitchen and living room are adorned with modern Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring, creating an inviting atmosphere. The master suite on the ground floor features a walk-in closet, and all bedrooms offer water view of the pond.    The kitchen is a chef's delight with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances, all from 2022. Beyond the home, the gated community offers a wealth of amenities, including a pristine pool, a playground, a dog park, and exterior maintenance. You'll also find gates and a dedicated community manager, along with 2 pickleball courts, a community pavilion, and an outdoor summer kitchen for memorable gatherings.    A rated schools like Gullett Elementary, Mona Jain Middle, and Lakewood Ranch High School are within a 4-mile radius. Plus, enjoy the convenience of being less than 10 minutes from Costco and mere moments away from groceries, restaurants, and shopping.    Don't miss your chance to experience this incredible blend of comfort, elegance, and community. Schedule a showing and make this dream home yours!
